metadata.name: Vitaldik
metadata.description: The first ever live auction of a stand-up comedian’s joke on the Ethereum blockchain created by AI and minted at ETHDenver 2023. This will be 1 of 2 NFTs minted based on this joke — the other will be the original video file of the performance by comedian, Leah Lamarr. Leah was awarded Entertainer of the Year by TIMEPieces x RobotosNFT in 2021.
